flag provided but not defined: -z
Usage of update-dnsmasq:
  -dir string
    	Override dnsmasq directory (default "/etc/dnsmasq.d")
  -f <file>
    	<file> # Load a config.boot file
  -h	Display help
  -safe
    	Fail over to /config/user-data/edgeos-adblock.failover.cfg
  -v	Verbose display
  -version
    	Show version
